    "@type": "FAQPage",
    "mainEntity": [
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Is TalentLMS or Skilljar better for customer training?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Skilljar is better for customer training. It was purpose-built for customer education with deep CRM integration (Salesforce, HubSpot, Gainsight), branded academy sites, content syndication, and built-in monetization. TalentLMS can train external users but wasn't designed for customer education at scale."
