        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Yes, TalentLMS can train external audiences through its branch system, but it wasn't designed for customer education at scale. The branding options don't match Skilljar's white-glove academy experience, and it lacks the deep CRM integrations that customer success teams need to prove training ROI."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "How does TalentLMS pricing compare to Skilljar?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "TalentLMS uses transparent, published pricing starting from free (5 users) to $449/month (Pro). Skilljar requires custom pricing through a sales consultation, with entry points significantly higher than TalentLMS — typically starting at $30,000+/year. TalentLMS is dramatically cheaper for internal training use cases."
        }
